    {
      "parameters": {
        "jsCode": "const results = [];\nconst inputs = $input.all();\nfor (let i = 0; i < inputs.length; i++) {\n  const data = inputs[i].json;\n  const firstName = (data['Seller Name'] && data['Seller Name'] !== 'N/A' && data['Seller Name'] !== '')\n    ? data['Seller Name'].split(' ')[0]\n    : 'there';\n\n  const message = 'Hi ' + firstName + ',\\n\\n'\n    + 'I noticed you\\'re advertising your property on Gumtree and just wanted to introduce myself.\\n\\n'\n    + 'With the increasing number of regulations in the rental sector and upcoming changes such as the Renters Reform Bill from 1st of May, many landlords are unaware of how many compliance rules now apply. Getting these wrong can result in significant fines or legal issues.\\n\\n'\n    + 'Such as providing tenants with a new information sheet from the government explaining tenancies moving to period \\u2014 if this is not done you can get fines up to \\u00a37,000.\\n\\n'\n    + 'If you\\'d find it helpful, I would be happy to run through the key compliance requirements and upcoming changes with you.\\n\\n'\n    + 'You can book a quick call here:\\nhttps://meetings.hubspot.com/dan648/gumtree-b2c-outreach-\\n\\n'\n    + 'Kind regards,\\nDan';\n\n  results.push({ json: Object.assign({}, data, { 'Draft Message': message, 'Status': 'Drafted' }) });\n}\nreturn results;"
      },
      "id": "77751d8b-054b-4324-bb31-c64829a92c8d",
      "name": "Build Message",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
